[I] QEMU Monitor Protocol library

[T] qemu.qmp is a QEMU Monitor Protocol ("QMP") library written in Python,
[T] using asyncio. It is used to send QMP messages to running QEMU emulators.

[U] https://pypi.org/project/qemu.qmp

